Venezuela’s Chavez Spoke With Putin About $4 Billion Loan

-- B y   J o s e   O r o z c o
-- 
2011-08-11T19:23:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-11/venezuela-s-chavez-spoke-with-putin-about-4-billion-loan.html
Venezuelan President  Hugo Chavez 
said he spoke with Russian Prime Minister  Vladimir Putin  to
“push forward” a $4 billion loan.  Chavez spoke by telephone in remarks broadcast by state
television.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jose Orozco in Caracas at 
